		<h1 class="display learn-h1">What is a<br>Backyard Ultra?</h1>
		<p class="learn-lede">One loop. 4.167 miles. Every hour. The last runner to finish a loop wins, even if they've run 300 miles to get there. Everyone else is a DNF.</p>

		<!-- Table of contents -->
